:"免責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用疫苗殺恐懼撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1784bd25a2f74c7668f70ee1ab210a5741712fd5","tid":2327504,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:31:16.000Z","msg":"藥厂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afac7193bdf700ee0859e8858c3dfcfe834abb8b","tid":2327504,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:33:08.000Z","msg":"打完死冇人需要負責<br />\n唔打中招有5000蚊收幾日出得院<br />\n你諗你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078f480a3202002c5d578761a99d6b8fafda87b3","tid":2327504,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:35:04.000Z","msg":"用左 支那鬼國生產既疫苗 出左事 <br />\n班狗官 邊敢追究<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e65bd133cfadd85a985d05b0de9cfffd1a10aaa","tid":2327504,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T08:36:25.000Z","msg":"你老尾陳肇始當香港人白老鼠.<br />\n<br />\n疫苗公司一般都會買保險, 以應對賠償問題.<br />\n即係呢間公司,無保險公司願意承擔風險.<br />\n<br />\n有事係政府負責. 點解係政府負責,唔係藥商負責.<br />\n既然無信心,就唔好用.<br />\n依家武肺死亡率少於1%."},{"pid":"c6a30b2a0c75f5dda59f6254bf53a786db9f9015","tid":2327504,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:12:36.000Z","msg":"責任全在__方"},{"pid":"f99dd3dce4d21e8fdf68c636eafb4ce7afee7ceb","tid":2327504,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:28:41.000Z","msg":"咁即係叫人唔好打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8886615a57db80d109814ac54a86a78afb8997b","tid":2327504,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa71614f1ed5f975da37c8e32b9fb7b6548aa913","tid":2327504,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"